<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4550196>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 18. Doubtful species. (a, b) Clathrocaspia sp., labelled as “Caspia microcingulifera, holotype”, locality 6 (ZIN, no number). (c–f) Clathrocaspia sp., labelled as “Caspia microcingulifera, paratype”, locality 9 (ZIN, no number). (g, h) Clathrocaspia valkanovi, holotype, locality 28 (ZIN 4367/1). (i) Clathrocaspia stanislavi, reconstruction of the holotype (after Alexenko and Starobogatov 1987), locality 30a. (j, k) Paratype of C. stanislavi, locality 30d (NMNH NASU, IKOFZ-It-167). (l) C. stanislavi, locality 30a (det. T.L. Alexenko; UGSB 25237). (m) C. stanislavi from Holocene deposits, locality 32 (IZAN, no number). Scale bars = 1 mm (a–d, g–m), 100 μm (e, f)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4550196/files/figure.png" .

